long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Void New Tab is a minimalist dark themed new tab page with a powerful search utility. For instructions on how to use Void, once installed type "help" into the search bar. Void is open source and proudly 100% free. You can find out more about Void and you can find its source code by typing "about" into the search bar.
